.TH MAN 1 "23 May 2022" "Experimental" "WHY MAN PAGE"
.SH NAME
why \- print a quotation from an E4S creator explaining why E4S was created. 
.SH SYNOPSIS
why [INDEX]
.SH DESCRIPTION
When why is run with no arguments it printos out a random quotation from one of the creators of E4S.
.SH OPTIONS
The options are as follows:

-#	Choose the index of the creator's answer you want.
.SH SEE ALSO
fortune(6)
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
Carter Grove (cgrove001@csbsju.edu)
